Synex is an asistant who maded for moderation stuff ,  music  , fun stuff  and economy 
if you want get all of his commands just type _help

all comands open list :
**Moderation Stuff**
_ban(banning member who you ping)

_warn(warnning pinged member)

_lock(locking channel)
_prefix(changes bot prefix)
_create-role(creates role)
**Fun**
_help(send dm message with commands)
_dm(it dm person who you pinged)
_meme(sending meme)
_serverinfo(sending iformation about server)
_covid(sending acctualy cases with covid-19)

_text(sending text in embed message)
_info(gives inforamation about pinged member)
_random(generates radom nuber from 1 to 1000000000)
_credits(sending dm with bot creator)
**Music #Beta**
_stop(stopping acctualy played music)
_skip(skipping acctualy played music)
_loop(looping actually playing music)
_np(finding what's playinng now)
_play(plays wideo)(link or name)
_volume(changing bot volume)
_join(after this command bot enter the autor command channel)
_leave(bot leave the channel)
**Economy **
_work(you can do this command 1 time a hour)
_bal(shows your balance)
_daily(daily reward)
_withraw(withdrawing momey from your account)
_dep(depositing money to your account)
